trans:
#print trans /-
@[trans]
theorem trans {H K L : subgroup G} (hhk : commensurable H K) (hkl : commensurable K L) : commensurable H L :=
  ⟨subgroup.relindex_ne_zero_trans hhk.1 hkl.1, subgroup.relindex_ne_zero_trans hkl.2 hhk.2⟩
#align trans trans
-/
symm:
#print symm /-
@[symm]
theorem symm {H K : subgroup G} : commensurable H K → commensurable K H :=
  And.symm
#align symm symm
-/

equivalence:
theorem equivalence : equivalence (@commensurable G _) :=
  ⟨commensurable.refl, fun _ _ => commensurable.symm, fun _ _ _ => commensurable.trans⟩
#align equivalence equivalence
eq:
theorem eq {H K : subgroup G} (hk : commensurable H K) : commensurator H = commensurator K :=
  subgroup.ext fun x =>
    let hx := (commensurable_conj x).1 hk
    ⟨fun h => hx.symm.trans (h.trans hk), fun h => hx.trans (h.trans hk.symm)⟩
#align eq eq

theorem commensurator_mem_iff (H : subgroup G) (g : G) :

#align commensurator_mem_iff commensurator_mem_iff

commensurable_inv:
/- ./././Mathport/Syntax/Translate/Expr.lean:207:4: warning: unsupported notation `«expr • » -/
/- ./././Mathport/Syntax/Translate/Expr.lean:207:4: warning: unsupported notation `«expr • » -/
theorem commensurable_inv (H : subgroup G) (g : conj_act G) :
    commensurable («expr • » g H) H ↔ commensurable H («expr • » g⁻¹ H) := by rw [commensurable_conj, inv_smul_smul]
#align commensurable_inv commensurable_inv
commensurable_conj:
/- ./././Mathport/Syntax/Translate/Expr.lean:207:4: warning: unsupported notation `«expr • » -/
/- ./././Mathport/Syntax/Translate/Expr.lean:207:4: warning: unsupported notation `«expr • » -/
theorem commensurable_conj {H K : subgroup G} (g : conj_act G) :
    commensurable H K ↔ commensurable («expr • » g H) («expr • » g K) :=
  and_congr (not_iff_not.mpr (eq.congr_left (cardinal.to_nat_congr (quot_conj_equiv H K g))))
    (not_iff_not.mpr (eq.congr_left (cardinal.to_nat_congr (quot_conj_equiv K H g))))
#align commensurable_conj commensurable_conj

theorem comm {H K : subgroup G} : commensurable H K ↔ commensurable K H :=
